# Prompt Version History

| Version | Date | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| v1.0 | 2026-04-15 | Bootstrap prompt suite created for deterministic AirMentor audit passes |
| v1.1 | 2026-04-15 | Added main analysis bootstrap prompt and operator-facing launch guidance |
| v2.0 | 2026-04-15 | Hardened bootstrap, pass prompts, and templates to require exhaustive route, role, feature, dependency, data, state, ML, test, UX, and live mapping before completion |
| v3.0 | 2026-04-15 | Added `exhaustive-closure-campaign.md` to drive closure-phase deep passes, continuity rules, remaining uncovered surfaces, and final completion gating |
| v3.1 | 2026-04-15 | Hardened `exhaustive-closure-campaign.md` so current blocker lists are treated as non-exhaustive seed evidence; added mandatory unknown-omission discovery, inventory cross-checking, and completeness verification rules |
| v3.2 | 2026-04-15 | Wired `exhaustive-closure-campaign.md` into future pass bundles by default and added the missing closure pass prompts for frontend microinteraction, backend provenance, workflow automation, script behavior, and same-student parity |
| v3.3 | 2026-04-15 | Prompt self-improvement hardening: upgraded `prompt-self-improvement-pass.md` to v2.1, upgraded bootstrap prompt to v2.1 with status-file truth precedence, and upgraded closure campaign prompt to v3.2 with explicit stale-assumption reconciliation against status/checkpoint/log artifacts |
| v4.0 | 2026-04-16 | Added `adversarial-validation-campaign.md` plus dedicated validation passes for claim verification, omission discovery, residual-gap closure, and closure-readiness verdicting; wired the validation layer into those pass bundles |

