## Downgrades Applied In Durable Files

- `audit-map/15-final-maps/data-flow-map.md` now explicitly states that the current content is partial overlay evidence, not a completed per-flow corpus.
- `audit-map/15-final-maps/feature-registry.md` now classifies `unlock-review` under the HoD surface and `queue-history` under a cross-role academic surface.
- `audit-map/04-feature-atoms/unlock-review-decision-flow.md` now records HoD-only route access instead of mentor-surface framing.
- `audit-map/04-feature-atoms/queue-history-filters-and-restore-actions.md` now records Course Leader/Mentor/HoD scope instead of mentor-only framing.
- `audit-map/25-accounts-routing/manual-action-required.md` no longer claims that `unattended-run-pass` is still non-terminal.

## Residual High-Risk Gaps

- A real standalone data-flow corpus is still missing.
- Same-student cross-surface parity remains unproven across mentor, course leader, HoD, sysadmin, and student surfaces.
- Authenticated live verification remains blocked by credentials plus current browser/network limits.
- UX conclusions remain inference-heavy rather than user-validated.

## Pass Output Contract

- Covered: architecture, role surfaces, feature registry, dependency graph, data flow, state flow, ML/risk/proof semantics, test posture, UX findings, and live-vs-local findings.
- Files updated: `audit-map/32-reports/claim-verification-matrix.md`, `audit-map/15-final-maps/data-flow-map.md`, `audit-map/15-final-maps/feature-registry.md`, `audit-map/04-feature-atoms/unlock-review-decision-flow.md`, `audit-map/04-feature-atoms/queue-history-filters-and-restore-actions.md`, `audit-map/23-coverage/coverage-ledger.md`, `audit-map/23-coverage/unreviewed-surface-list.md`, `audit-map/24-agent-memory/working-knowledge.md`, `audit-map/14-reconciliation/reconciliation-log.md`, `audit-map/14-reconciliation/contradiction-matrix.md`, `audit-map/25-accounts-routing/manual-action-required.md`, `audit-map/32-reports/audit-air-mentor-ui-bootstrap-claim-verification-pass.last-message.md`.
- Remains uncovered: standalone per-flow data-flow entries, unknown-omission audit, closure-readiness verdict, same-student parity, authenticated live proof.
