2. continue to `cost-optimization-pass`, then `unattended-run-pass`, then Phase B closure deep passes (`frontend-microinteraction-pass`, `backend-provenance-pass`, `workflow-automation-pass`, `script-behavior-pass`, `same-student-cross-surface-parity-pass`) with the corrected routing baseline carried forward explicitly

