+- `air-mentor-api/scripts/generate-academic-parity-seed.ts` exists to build cross-surface parity fixtures, but the current audit has not traced its consumers, freshness, or relationship to live/admin proof data.
+- Live auth and recovery helper scripts (`system-admin-live-auth`, teaching password probing, closeout artifact snapshotting, Railway recovery) are present but not yet mapped, so the intended recovery path from deployment drift is still only partially understood.
